  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in posterior lumbar fusion. The model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed for intended use in pre-market submission support for Class II spinal fixation devices under 21 CFR 888.3070. One factor (Test conditions) falls below the required credibility level due to a single test condition evaluated; all remaining factors meet or exceed required levels.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/f1717-compression-bending-static",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/fea-predicts-f1717-stiffness-and-yield",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/model/pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v3",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/f1717-lab1-experimental-n6",
    "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/f1717-lab2-experimental-n5"
  ],
